         <div type="translation">
 	<p>This image of the Bhagavant is the pious gift of the <foreign>śākyabhikṣu</foreign> Buddhaghoṣa, the guardian of the great <foreign>Gandhakuṭi</foreign> and the pupil of the reverend Dharmmavatsa, [his] instructor, an expert in the Three <foreign>Piṭakas</foreign>, who acts in accordance with the Teaching of the Bhagavant, the Buddha. </p>
